metadata.name: Doge Couch
metadata.description:
Own the throne of the greatest meme of all time, Doge. For the past decade plus, this couch has been one of Kabuso’s (Doge’s) favorite spots to hang out.  

The couch auction is for an NFT which represents physical ownership of the couch and can be redeemed to take possession of the actual couch. 

Doge smell included free of charge.

To organize delivery of the couch, please contact: info@pleasr.org.
